Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.30,0:08:43.01,Elsee,,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.99,0:08:46.62,Keima,,0000,0000,0000,,yahoo～这个…这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.82,0:08:47.29,Keima,,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.73,0:08:48.31,Keima,,0000,0000,0000,,还有这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.58,0:08:49.25,Keima,,0000,0000,0000,,这个也要…
